:63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"發功委可恥！"},{"pid":"77952a1f57317629e28f15499f53c33342ffd9c2","tid":1149083,"uid":58305,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"fb85ba1a2ab767fa98a9fea03d2da454724d8d3c","tid":1149083,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"Stephen Curry手指脫臼問題比想像中更為嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n根據知名記者Sam Amick表示，Curry在火箭系列戰G2左手中指脫臼給予他的影響，遠比他表現出的更加嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n⬛從G2開始，Curry三分命中率沒有一場超過30%<br />\n⬛四戰下來三分命中率僅25.5%<br />\n⬛就連罰球都開始失準，中止連7場100%命中率<br />\n<br />\n⬜本季季後賽在與火箭系列戰G2前，Curry三分命中率46.6%、罰球97.6%，此對比下來有巨大落差。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n就目前G6上半場看下來，Curry的狀態仍舊不好，且還犯規纏身，半場0分2助攻3犯，這對他來講的確打擊不小，但好在Klay Thompson有跳了出來，Kevon Looney持續在籃下建功，加上火箭感覺很沒把這場當生死戰的感覺，防守與籃板保護的都不是很好....<br />\n<br />\n然而受傷不會是超級巨星輸球的藉口，Curry亦是如此，因此在KD缺陣下，將考驗Curry如何克服自身低迷的三分命中率，找回自己引以為傲的招牌武器，就看下半場可不可以打出反彈。<br />\n<br />\n至於休士頓火箭，下半場一定要把籃板保護好，這樣大好利多的情況假使真的沒拿下，那就真的沒辦法了....<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n⬛我的Instagram﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿<br />\n➡ <a href=\"http://t.cn/EirREeu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.cn%2FEirREeu&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=4a970c0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.cn/EirREeu</a><br />\n✏️ HBK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca34f6d36315fbea427471cc7c41287f631613c","tid":1149083,"uid":66769,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:49:01.000Z","msg":"打面打到啪啪聲"},{"pid":"288be018062582d393fa8385f3022c53262e4ee3","tid":1149083,"uid":34087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019